<P>AN ABRIDGMENT OF THE <HI>English</HI> MILITARY Discipline, <HI>Compiled by the</HI> Late <HI>Duke of</HI> Monmouth.</P>
<P><HI>Printed by Especial Command, for the Use of Their</HI> Majesties <HI>Forces.</HI></P>
