<P>Printed at <HI>London,</HI> by their <HI>Majesties</HI> Printers; Reprinted at <HI>Boston</HI> by <HI>Samuel Green,</HI> And Sold by <HI>Sam. Phillips</HI> at the west end of the Exchange 1690.</P>
</DIV1>
