<ITEM><HI>Poise your Muskets.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Order your Muskets.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Pikemen take heed.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><PB N="12" REF="000508_0011_0FA6A7A681C73340">
