<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<ITEM><HI>advance your Pikes.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Shoulder your Pikes.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Charge to the Front.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Charge to the Right.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Charge to the Right about.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
