<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><PB N="13" REF="000508_0012_0FA6A7A959D92060">
<HI>Charge to the Left about.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>as you were.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Port.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Comport.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Charge to the Front.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Trail.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Charge as you were.</HI></ITEM>
